I"²<p>Processflows are the diagrammatic representation of a business process. As an organization, you can have a number of business processes which you need to perform your daily activities. The workflow management screen will allow you to search, filter, create, edit workflows.</p>

<p>By reading this document an implementer would be able to design the first processslow for an organization and will execute it from the web portal also.</p>

